
format_linux.sh install 
    step1: mkdir ~/bin
    step2: cp -ar foramt* ~/bin
           cp -ar astyle ~/bin
    step3:
           echo "export PATH=~/bin:${PATH}" >> ~/.bashrc
How to use it:
    Go to the code directory;
    runing:
            format_linux.sh xxx.cpp 
            format_linux.sh xxx.h
            format_linux.sh *.c
            format_linux.sh *.*
            .....
